			To Do

			 1.1

		      By pikpik


Description

	A simple To Do list, for the shell.


Usage

	todo

	Prints a listing of reminders.


	todo "[args]"

	Appends a reminder to the list.


	did "[args]"

	Removes a reminder with text containing "args."


Requirements

	The Almquist Shell

Platforms

	MINIX 3.2.0

	NetBSD 5.1


Installation

	Feel free to adjust paths to your liking.


	Append the following to ~/.profile:

	. $HOME/todo.sh


	If necessary,

	touch ~/.reminders

	chmod u+rw ~/.reminders


